#

Crispy Tofu Sliders

35 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuick

Description

Delicious crispy tofu served in soft sliders with fresh toppings and a zesty sauce.

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 1 block
  • slider buns: 4
  • panko breadcrumbs: 1 cup
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • cornstarch: 2 tablespoons
  • oil (for frying): as needed
  • lettuce leaves: 4 leaves
  • tomato, sliced: 1
  • avocado, sliced: 1
  • spicy mayo or sauce: to taste
